Ornate Corridor~
Some fanatic must have spent years carving out this portion of the
catacombs.  The walls are gorgeously sculpted to resemble fine hardwood
panelling, polished to a glossy hue.  If you had not touched the
silvery grey oaken wall, you would have never realized it was actually
cold stone.  What purpose could this have possibly served in the grand
scheme of things?
