  {BO,M}You are blinded almost immediately upon entering this room by the
  reflection of you lamps from hundreds of amethysts encrusted in the
  walls of this area.  While your eyes become adjusted to the violet
  glare from the room, you begin to notice the air is much drier than it
  had been.  Surrounding you on the floor are numerous mottled reptiles
  in purple hues.{bo,m}
  
  
