#31948
{BO,M} Hall of Amethyst{bo,m}~
  
  {BO,M}The culmination of the passage is a grand hall carved from the inside 
  of a giant amethyst crystal.  You can see only the deep purple depths
  of this astounding phenomenon, making you wonder exactly how large this
  could be.  The lack of humidity has become unbearable by this point,
  your entire body feeling parched and weak.  Curled around itself, a
  large dragon slumbers fitfully.  Throbbing echoes of the dragon's
  heartbeat and breathing fill the room.{bo,m}


