  behold.  A grove of trees somehow is growing underground in the
  catacombs.  But these trees are nothing like those above ground with
  their organic leaves.  The trunks are of pure silver, and from the
  foliage a soft tinkling sound comes from the brushing of emerald leaves
  upon each other.  As you walk through the grove, you spy a clearing a
  bit to the north.{bo,g}
  
  
