#31962
{BO,G}Emerald Gates{bo,g}~
  
  
  {BO,G}The grove of unusual trees parts here to reveal three sets
  of burnished steel gates. The gates are inlaid with an emerald
  mosaic depicting a dragon in various positions.  To the north,
  the dragon is rampant, clawing the air with its forelegs.  To the 
  west, the mosaic shows the dragon with wings extended in flight.
  To the east, the dragon is lounging on a mountaintop basking in
  the sun.  Hovering above the three gates are tiny iridescent green
  dragons peering down at you curiously.  {bo,g}
  
  
