{BO,GREEN}Emerald Gazebo{bo,green}~
  
  
  {BO,G}Embraced within the boughs of this grandmother of all trees is the
  gazebo in which you now stand. Tendrils of the tree's own branches lace
  together to form the walls of the gazebo, and thankfully provide enough
  cover to shelter you from the pounding rain.  Draped across the central
  beam of the gazebo, the green dragon blends well with the emerald
  foliage.  Amazingly, it's ponderous weight does not topple the
  precariously perched structure
 {bo,g}
  
  
