#31973
{BO,BLUE}Sapphire Dock{bo,blue}~
  
  
  {BO,BLUE}You stand on a pier of a single sapphire jutting out into an expanse of
  sparkling blue water.  Rising from the mirror placid lake are spears of
  sapphire, pointing in various directions or clustered into mini-islets.
  Your breath puffs as you exhale, the frigid air causing it to frost.
  You become decidedly chilly when your clothes drenched from the emerald
  forest begin to freeze.
