{BO,W}Spires of Sapphire{bo,w}~
  
  
  {BO,CYAN}Here the sapphire spears form an elaborate lattice and as a whole
  resemble a tower with three primary spires.  The air is bitterly cold
  in this area, and snow blankets the isle and dusts the spires
  themselves with highlights of white.  Nestled amidst the three spires
  is a blue dragon, whose eyes are no more than a pair of icy chips
  against its deep blue hide.  It raises its head and swivels it to
  inspect you as you alight upon its island.{bo,cyan}
  
  
