{BO,WHITE}Crystalline Cavern{bo,white}~
  
  
  {BO,WHITE}After the darkness of the burrows, your eyes are dazzled by the sudden
  spray of rainbow colored light.  At some point the vein of clear
  crystal that surrounds you must reach the surface to be able to refract
  sunlight this far underground.  Gorgeous blocks and shapes of naturally
  fractured crystal decorate the cavern from floor to ceiling.  Your nose
  cringes at the scent of sulfur in the air, and the orange glow to the
  south overpowers the softer tones of the rainbows.{bo,white}
  
  
